:"닥쳐 네가 자꾸 달라붙으니까 이 지경이 된 거잖아","timestamp":"2026-04-28T09:16:14.589Z","roundId":"group_round_1777367753080_hn4fhex","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777345325424","_id":13026,"deleted":true},{"id":1777376283863,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"680d8570-6b8c-4be8-a5a3-af0f1f47b8e5","senderName":"金硕珍","text":"닥쳐 네가 자꾸 달라붙으니까 이 지경이 된 거잖아","timestamp":"2026-04-28T09:16:15.266Z","translation":"闭嘴 就是你老贴上去才搞成这样的","roundId":"group_round_1777367753080_hn4fhex","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777345325424","_id":13027},{"id":1777376283864,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"17c4b1e6-f9c4-432a-9430-6f7e9b476493","senderName":"田柾国","text":"听到这话猛地咬紧下巴 拳头攥得咯吱响 但没有反驳","timestamp":"2026-04-28T09:16:15.776Z","roundId":"group_round_1777367753080_hn4fhex","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777345325424","_id":13028},{"id":1777376283865,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"17c4b1e6-f9c4-432a-9430-6f7e9b476493","senderName":"田柾国","text":"低下头死死盯着地毯上的纹路 喉咙里挤出一声几乎听不见的","timestamp":"2026-04-28T09:16:16.237Z","roundId":"group_round_1777367753080_hn4fhex","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777345325424","_id":13029},{"id":1777376283866,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"17c4b1e6-f9c4-432a-9430-6f7e9b476493","senderName":"田柾国","text":"……나도 알아","timestamp":"2026-04-28T09:16:16.655Z","roundId":"group_round_1777367753080_hn4fhex","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777345325424","_id":13030,"deleted":true},{"id":1777376283867,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"17c4b1e6-f9c4-432a-9430-6f7e9b476493","senderName":"田柾国","text":"……나도 알아","timestamp":"2026-04-28T09:16:17.430Z","translation":"……我也知道","roundId":"group_round_1777367753080_hn4fhex","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777345325424","_id":13031},{"id":"sys_1777370682784_ea","sender":"system","type":"system_notice","text":"金硕珍 將群名改為「作战会议：绝对不能让她搬走」","timestamp":"2026-04-28T10:04:42.784Z","roundId":"group_round_1777370520308_e64rpi3","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777306659998","_id":13032},{"id":1777379265296,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"17c4b1e6-f9c4-432a-9430-6f7e9b476493","senderName":"田柾国","text":"表情包：瘫（化成水）","timestamp":"2026-04-28T10:04:42.999Z","sticker":"https://files.catbox.moe/1l45zi.gif","stickerMeaning":"瘫（化成水）","roundId":"group_round_1777370520308_e64rpi3","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777306659998","_id":13033},{"id":1777379265297,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"17c4b1e6-f9c4-432a-9430-6f7e9b476493","senderName":"田柾国","text":"형... 진짜 누나 나가는 거 아니겠지? 나 방에서 혼자 돌아버릴 거 같아...","timestamp":"2026-04-28T10:04:43.220Z","translation":"哥……姐姐不会真的要搬出去吧？我一个人在房间里快疯了……","roundId":"group_round_1777370520308_e64rpi3","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777306659998","_id":13034},{"id":1777379265298,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"680d8570-6b8c-4be8-a5a3-af0f1f47b8e5","senderName":"金硕珍","text":"네가 옆에서 계속 귀찮게 구니까 화나신 거잖아.","timestamp":"2026-04-28T10:04:43.585Z","translation":"还不是因为你一直在旁边烦她，她才生气的。","roundId":"group_round_1777370520308_e64rpi3","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777306659998","_id":13035},{"id":1777379265299,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"17c4b1e6-f9c4-432a-9430-6f7e9b476493","senderName":"田柾国","text":"형도 아까 누나 손 닦는다고 억지 부렸으면서! 지금 누구 탓할 때야 ㅠㅠ 어떻게 풀지?","timestamp":"2026-04-28T10:04:43.772Z","translation":"哥刚才还不是硬拉着姐姐的手擦个没完！现在是互相怪罪的时候吗ㅠㅠ 到底怎么让她消气啊？","roundId":"group_round_1777370520308_e64rpi3","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777306659998","_id":13036},{"id":1777379265300,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"680d8570-6b8c-4be8-a5a3-af0f1f47b8e5","senderName":"金硕珍","text":"하아... 일단 저녁은 내가 준비할게. 아까 약 부작용 때문에 빈속이셨으니까 맛있는 거라도 해드려야지.","timestamp":"2026-04-28T10:04:44.097Z","translation":"唉……晚饭我来准备。她之前因为药的副作用一直空着肚子，总得做点好吃的看能不能哄哄她。","roundId":"group_round_1777370520308_e64rpi3","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777306659998","_id":13037},{"id":1777379265301,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"680d8570-6b8c-4be8-a5a3-af0f1f47b8e5","senderName":"金硕珍","text":"넌 그냥 방에 가만히 처박혀 있어. 또 눈앞에서 얼쩡거리면 진짜 짐 싸실지도 모르니까.","timestamp":"2026-04-28T10:04:44.336Z","translation":"你就老老实实待在你房间里别出来。再在她面前晃悠，她可能真的要收拾行李了。","roundId":"group_round_1777370520308_e64rpi3","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777306659998","_id":13038},{"id":1777379265302,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"17c4b1e6-f9c4-432a-9430-6f7e9b476493","senderName":"田柾国","text":"형 근데... 누나 지금 그 약 때문에 아예 밥을 못 먹잖아. 이따가 차려놔도 그냥 안 먹겠다고 하면 어떡해?","timestamp":"2026-04-28T10:09:44.183Z","translation":"哥但是... 姐姐现在因为那个药根本吃不下饭啊。到时候要是做好了她可能直接不吃怎么办？","roundId":"group_round_1777370945414_388jt7h","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777306659998","_id":13039},{"id":1777379265303,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"680d8570-6b8c-4be8-a5a3-af0f1f47b8e5","senderName":"金硕珍","text":"하... 그러니까 미치겠다는 거야. 아까 점심도 파스타 몇 입 먹고 다 남겼잖아.","timestamp":"2026-04-28T10:09:44.615Z","translation":"哈... 所以我才快疯了啊。刚才午饭也是，意面吃了几口就全剩下了。","roundId":"group_round_1777370945414_388jt7h","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777306659998","_id":13040},{"id":1777379265304,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"17c4b1e6-f9c4-432a-9430-6f7e9b476493","senderName":"田柾国","text":"表情包：怨念","timestamp":"2026-04-28T10:09:44.841Z","sticker":"https://files.catbox.moe/6ujxc2.gif","stickerMeaning":"怨念","roundId":"group_round_1777370945414_388jt7h","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777306659998","_id":13041},{"id":1777379265305,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"17c4b1e6-f9c4-432a-9430-6f7e9b476493","senderName":"田柾国","text":"진짜 그 약 내가 몰래 찾아서 다 변기에 버릴까? 밥 안 먹고 쓰러지면 어떡해 ㅠㅠ","timestamp":"2026-04-28T10:09:45.115Z","translation":"真的要不我偷偷把那药找出来全扔马桶里冲了吧？不吃饭晕倒了怎么办ㅠㅠ","roundId":"group_round_1777370945414_388jt7h","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777306659998","_id":13042},{"id":"sys_1777370985266_mt","sender":"system","type":"system_notice","text":"金硕珍 將群名改為「作战会议：必须让她吃下晚饭」","timestamp":"2026-04-28T10:09:45.267Z","roundId":"group_round_1777370945414_388jt7h","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777306659998","_id":13043},{"id":1777379265306,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"680d8570-6b8c-4be8-a5a3-af0f1f47b8e5","senderName":"金硕珍","text":"약 버리는 건 내가 알아서 할 테니까 넌 나서지 마. 또 누나 화나게 해서 진짜 집 나가시면 네가 책임질 거야?","timestamp":"2026-04-28T10:09:45.591Z","translation":"扔药的事我会看着办的，你别出头。要是又惹姐姐生气让她真搬出去了，你负得起责吗？","roundId":"group_round_1777370945414_388jt7h","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777306659998","_id":13044},{"id":1777379265307,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"680d8570-6b8c-4be8-a5a3-af0f1f47b8e5","senderName":"金硕珍","text":"일단 속 안 부대끼는 수프라도 끓여볼 테니까... 넌 이따가 누나 나오면 쓸데없는 소리 하지 말고 조용히 밥 먹는 분위기나 맞춰.","timestamp":"2026-04-28T10:09:46.191Z","translation":"我先去熬点不伤胃的汤试试... 等会儿姐姐出来你别说废话，安静点配合吃饭的气氛就行。","roundId":"group_round_1777370945414_388jt7h","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777306659998","_id":13045},{"id":1777379265308,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"17c4b1e6-f9c4-432a-9430-6f7e9b476493","senderName":"田柾国","text":"알았어... 방에 가만히 있을게. 근데 형, 만약에 이따가 밥 다 됐는데 누나가 문 안 열어주면 어떡해...?","timestamp":"2026-04-28T10:19:20.309Z","translation":"知道了……我会乖乖待在房间里的。但是哥，万一待会饭做好了，姐姐不给开门怎么办……？","roundId":"group_round_1777371399862_ra9l0r3","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777306659998","_id":13046},{"id":1777379265309,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"680d8570-6b8c-4be8-a5a3-af0f1f47b8e5","senderName":"金硕珍","text":"열어줄 때까지 문 밖에서 무릎 꿇고 빌어야지. 너 아까처럼 막 매달리면서 울지 마. 누나 더 질려하시니까.","timestamp":"2026-04-28T10:19:21.330Z","translation":"那就在门外跪着求她直到她开门为止。你别像刚才那样死缠着她哭。姐姐会更烦的。","roundId":"group_round_1777371399862_ra9l0r3","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777306659998","_id":13047},{"id":1777379265310,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"17c4b1e6-f9c4-432a-9430-6f7e9b476493","senderName":"田柾国","text":"안 울어... 형 나 지금 누나가 방에서 캐리어 싸고 있을까 봐 심장 터질 거 같아...","timestamp":"2026-04-28T10:19:21.695Z","translation":"我不哭……哥，我现在好怕姐姐在房间里收拾行李，心脏都要炸了……","roundId":"group_round_1777371399862_ra9l0r3","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777306659998","_id":13048},{"id":1777379265311,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"680d8570-6b8c-4be8-a5a3-af0f1f47b8e5","senderName":"金硕珍","text":"재수 없는 소리 하지 마. 상상만 해도 돌아버릴 것 같으니까.","timestamp":"2026-04-28T10:19:21.929Z","translation":"别乌鸦嘴。光是想想我都要疯了。","roundId":"group_round_1777371399862_ra9l0r3","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777306659998","_id":13049},{"id":"sys_1777371562191_14","sender":"system","type":"announcement","authorName":"金硕珍","announcementPreview":"[공지] 오늘 저녁 목표: 양송이 수프 반 그릇 이상 먹이기. 절대 심기 건드리지 말 것.","announcementId":"ann_1777371562188","text":"📢 金硕珍 發布了群公告","timestamp":"2026-04-28T10:19:22.191Z","roundId":"group_round_1777371399862_ra9l0r3","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777306659998","_id":13050},{"id":1777379265312,"sender":"them","senderCharId":"17c4b1e6-f9c4-432a-9430-6f7e9b476493","senderName":"田柾国","text":"나 몰래 누나 방문에 귀 좀 대보고 올게... 짐 싸는 소리 나면 진짜 문 부수고 들어갈 거야.","timestamp":"2026-04-28T10:19:22.498Z","translation":"我去偷偷贴在姐姐门上听一下动静……要是听到收拾行李的声音，我真的会破门进去的。","roundId":"group_round_1777371399862_ra9l0r3","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"group_1777306659998","_id":13051},{"id":1777370265297,"sender":"them","text":"누나...","timestamp":1777372259230,"tempo":"S","translation":"姐姐……","rawContent":"누나... || 姐姐……","roundId":"round_1777372237044_dyqzwpl1p","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","characterId":"17c4b1e6-f9c4-432a-9430-6f7e9b476493","_id":13052},{"id":1777370265298,"sender":"them","text":"아직 화 많이 났어...?","timestamp":1777372260732,"tempo":"S","translation":"还在生很大的气吗……？","rawContent":"아직 화 많이 났어...? || 还在生很大的气吗……？","roundId":"round_1777372237044_dyqzwpl1p","userId":"uid_1777278796737_if0t11hik","chara